sentence: The primary effectors of Gβγ are various ion channels, such as G protein-coupled inwardly-rectifying potassium channel (GIRKs), P-type calcium channel / Q-type calcium channel - and N- type voltage-gated Casup2 + / sup channels, as well as some isoforms of AC and PLC, along with some phosphoinositide-3-kinase (PI3K) isoforms.
